{"tid":467301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓士兵經板門店投奔南韓途中被槍傷","createTime":"2017-11-13T11:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T12:40:45.000Z","uid":26331,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"05f51c5793420b152d0aa4808acc344b3a42a8c9","tid":467301,"uid":26331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:24:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】南韓軍方公布，一名北韓士兵經兩韓邊境的板門店變節投奔南韓，被北韓部隊開槍擊傷。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社引述南韓聯合參謀本部報道，該名士兵是在今日下午，由板門店北韓一方的哨站走過來投奔南韓，途中被北韓部隊開槍擊中，進入南韓一方後隨即被送往醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n板門店位於兩韓邊境非軍事區，周邊是共同安全區，南北韓雙方在各自的一方有士兵執勤戒備。<br />\n<br />\n南韓軍方表示，一直有提高警覺防範北韓作出軍事挑釁，目前處於全面戒備狀態。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=243030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D243030&d=Wqqs1%2FQuREATe5Sljs4VVwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=6cb8897e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D243030&h=5b2615ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=243030</a>"},{"pid":"d574d94ab7603d985b89ef5116946b1aea86dd63","tid":467301,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"北韓士兵渣到開槍都射毋死人"},{"pid":"00123fab9565cb5299b4a052cf4e7ec145f8ec8f","tid":467301,"uid":156283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48b580d7aa7c1c0878edf3676b3a5ed713dd392b","tid":467301,"uid":38988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北韓士兵渣到開槍都射毋死人</blockquote><br />\n餓呀 冇力射唔準佢個撚頭嘛"},{"pid":"827b9ee2701155a2659da5c6763400fa55931592","tid":467301,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>北韓士兵渣到開槍都射毋死人</blockquote><br />\n餓呀 冇力射唔準佢個撚頭嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔射分分鐘畀金仔送去勞改或者餵狗<br />\n老閪都射啦<br />\n最多射歪少少"},{"pid":"18